OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRussian threat means UK    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Farmy needs more cash, says 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FBen Wallace                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Defence Secretary Ben Wallace has urged
OL,6, the prime minister to increase spending
OL,7, on the UK's armed forces in light of   
OL,8, Russia's invasion of Ukraine.          
OL,10,FIn a speech, he said funding must react
OL,11,Fto the "direct" threat Russia poses to 
OL,12,FEurope.                                
OL,14,FThe UK currently spends around 2% of   
OL,15,Fits GDP on defence, matching the target
OL,16,FNato sets for its members.             
OL,18,FBut Mr Wallace has reportedly written  
OL,19,Fto the PM asking for an increase to    
OL,20,F2.5% by 2028.                          
